The office shall include the following divisions, each of which shall be headed by a director appointed by the secretary pursuant to KRS 12.050:
The Division of Finance and Personnel, which shall provide financial, personnel, facility, and contract administration services;
The Compliance Division, which shall monitor incentives and collect and maintain data on incentives after they are awarded;
The Incentive Assistance Division, which shall coordinate necessary documentation and assist the Department for Business Development in preparing recommendations and finalizing documents for presentation to the authority or other body for consideration and approval; and
The Division of Network Administration, which shall coordinate internal information technology needs.
